title: Golden Age of Video Games - Age of the Cartridge v2.4
description:
This is the Age of the Cartridge collection v2.4, which features all the cartridge-based games from the Golden Age of Video Games, including the Game Boy, Game Gear, NES, Sega Master System, MSX, SNES, Sega Genesis, Sega 32X, TurboGrafx, Neo Geo, GBA, and N64 game collections!

What is the Golden Age of Video Games?

Well, I spent over ten years researching and playing full game collections (over 10,000 games) of previous generations of video game systems to create a collection that I feel represents the "golden age of video games". With this collection, posterity may now play a nearly comprehensive collection of the best classic games (even the translated and obscure ones) without tons of research or sorting through full ROM collections that are 90% crud.

Please seed and enjoy!
